reviewText: Much too violent for my tastes.  Story lines are okay, but it won't raise your spirits if you want to leave a movie feeling uplifted.

I am a Travolta fan, so when I saw this collection, I just knew I had to order it.  I am so glad I did, it's a great set.  Face Off and the General's Daughter are my favorites, so I'm glad to have this set as a part of my DVD collection, and you can't beat the price!
